# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.
See [Conventional Commits](https://conventionalcommits.org) for commit guidelines.

## [1.1.0] (2019-09-05)


### Features

* Adding access control ([#20](https://github.com/cennznet/singlesource-extension/issues/20))


### Breaking changes

* DApp using single-source extension now need to call enable() to get access.
Previous:
const singleSource = window.SingleSource
Now:
const singleSource = window.cennznetInjected['singleSource'].enable()





## [1.0.0]


### Features

* Connect with mySingleSource mobile app
* Check balances
* Transactions history
* Sign transaction
* Switch environment
